I get these potions wholesale from the healers!
What? No, that potion is still good! They get better with age, like wine.

You've got a very serviceable fishing pole there. I wouldn't try catching large fish with it, but it's a perfect beginner's pole.
Bring me a Golem Jo or Wood Golem Heart and I'll assemble your fishing pole. Hope to see you fishing soon.
You're giving your heart to me? Bwahaha, just joking, this should make a nice pole. I'll just carve it and assemble your fishing pole. Wait here a moment.

There you go. The string part with the hook goes into the water and you hold onto the stick part. I can't tell you how many beginner fisherman just toss the whole thing into the water. Of course they always claim they lost it to some huge whale or something.
Oh, you found one! Nice length, good flex, aye this will do nicely. One moment while I assemble your fishing pole.
There you go. You'll want to watch out for that hook, it gets caught on things pretty easily and when you catch it on a neighboring fisherman they get a little annoyed, hehe.

Oh, I guess you don't need this. If you already have your fishing pole, just give me a C note and I'll license you to go fishing for the day. The license covers all fishing holes run by the Department of Fish and Games.
Don't know why you want other people knowin' you're the master of catchin' small fish, but it's up to you.
You really do have a knack for catchin those little guys.
Arrrr, you're gettin' ta be a mighty fine fisherman.
Congratulations, you now know which end of the fishin' pole to hold.

Some day, I may even tell you how I lost my hand here... What's that... well, no, I didn't actually lose my hand, but it was a close one. Just don't trust that you'll always pull a harmless fish out of the water. Yarrr!
Tackle Master says, Listen up all you bottom feeders! %s has earned the title Pro Fisherman! You could learn a thing or two from them, yes sir.
By the way, these fish don't count towards a Fish Title Token. They are way too common and easy to catch.
You should be all set to start fishing now. Good luck and remember a true fisherman releases the small catches.
Welcome back chum! Do you need a fishing license today? Just give me a C note and I'll get you all signed up and ready to fish.

You should be all set to start fishing now. Good luck and remember the minnow released today is the big catch of tomorrow. Well, not literally tomorrow, it takes a while for the fish to get big enough, but you know what I mean.
You're all set, I renewed your license for another day.
Welcome back! You'll be wanting a license...
Hmmm, money... put you down on the list... Ok, you're licensed for the day.
Don't forget that I'll buy your catch if you're willing to sell. Good luck and remember to throw the small ones back.
You catch'em, I release'em. Come again!
Hey, you caught 600 Minnows?!!! You just can't catch enough of these little fishies can you? Ok Skipper, I guess you deserve a prize.
You caught 100 Guppies? Not bad, I bet you have quite a collection... unless you eat them. Yuck, guppy breath!
You caught 100 Mollies? Good job! I like them so much that I made a pond for mine at home. Maybe I'll show you how to make one someday.
I see you've learned a thing or two about fishing. You're becoming quite good at this. Not every fisherman catches 100 fish. It takes determination and skill it does. Here, have your reward.
My oh my! I'm truly impressed. You caught yourself 300 Large Fish. You're really becoming a pro at this. Here's your reward my friend.
Hey, would you mind showing me your technique someday?
You need three things to be a good fisherman.

First, you need a fishing pole. I can make one for you, but I'll need a Golem Jo or a Wood Golem Heart to assemble it. I remember my first fishing pole, it was just a stick with some string. I couldn't catch a cold with that thing.
Second, you need a fishing license. I sell licenses for a C note, allowing you to fish for a whole day.
And last, you need patience. Just enjoy the peace that fishing brings and talk to your fellow fisherman, but don't believe all their fish stories, heh.
Here take this fishing guide. It has everything you need to know.
I see you're already licensed to fish. Make sure you have your rod ready and don't crowd the other fisherman. If you still need to get a fishing pole, I'll give you the instructions for a few pyreal.
I license fisherman for a C note. That covers you for an entire day.
If you still need help getting ready to fish I sell a good beginner's fishing guide for only a few coins. Just hand me whatever you can and I'll give you a guide.
I license fisherman for a C note if you care to fish. The license covers all fishing holes run by the Department of Fish and Games.
So you want to go fishing, eh? Ok then, lets see here...

You know, I used to fish back in Ispar. One time I had this giant fish on the line and it was a real fighter. Had to lash... oh, right, sorry, you're all set. Remember the license is only good for a day, so catch a big one before then!

Oh, I also supply the local grocers with fresh fish, so I'll buy your catch from you if you like. I pay a lot more than most grocers will, because I know the fish are fresh. Good luck and remember to throw the small ones back.
You caught 400 Minnows? That's not very impressive, but I suppose I should give you something. Here take this and try catching some bigger fish. I'll just release these little ones.
You know, I just have to release these little ones. Why do you bother to keep catching these anyway? Have you heard of a thing called catch and release?
